<span id="fn_303"></span>[59:3](sbe24033.htm#fr_307.md) TD2 has only 'three
hundred years,' by the accidental omission of a cipher; it also omits
the months and days.

<span id="fn_304"></span>[59:4](sbe24033.htm#fr_308.md) See Vend. II, 16,
