gôharî*k*-î pîr va*l* *s*êdân lâ. yehabûntô.'

<span id="fn_313"></span>[61:1](sbe24033.htm#fr_318.md) See Chap. VIII, 29.

<span id="fn_314"></span>[61:2](sbe24033.htm#fr_319.md) The demon of wrath
