<span id="fn_331"></span>[63:4](sbe24033.htm#fr_336.md) Darmesteter (SBE,
vol. xxiii, p. 295, note 4) identifies this name with Pathana of
Zamyâ*d* Yt. 41, which seems to mean 'highwayman;' but this
